body:
Hi {{ user.name }},
    Thank you for your order! Your order number is {{ order.id }}.
Items:
{% for item in order.items %}
- {{ item.name }}: ${{ item.price }}
{% endfor %}

Total: ${{ order.total }}

Hi {{ user.name }},

We are excited to announce a new feature: {{ feature.name }}!

{{ feature.description }}

You can learn more about it here: {{ feature_link }}

Hi {{ new_user.name }},
{{ inviter.name }} has invited you to join the {{ organization.name }} organization. Click the link below to accept the invitation:
{{ invitation_link }}
